# Prevent new root-level Markdown files (use docs/ folder instead)
# Allowed root docs: README.md, CHANGELOG.md, CONTRIBUTING.md, SECURITY.md, LICENSE
# Exception: EXECUTION_PATTERNS.md is auto-generated from execution logs and should be tracked
/*.md
!/README.md
!/CHANGELOG.md
!/CONTRIBUTING.md
!/SECURITY.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/CODEOWNERS
!/EXECUTION_PATTERNS.md
